== Emotional Freedom Techniques (EFT)
_Source: EFT International_

#inner-work[
  *The Tapping Sequence:*
  Used primarily in Year 1 to clear "psychic debris" and stabilize the astral body before laboratory operations.
  1. *The Setup:* Tap the "Karate Chop" point while stating the issue and accepting oneself.
  2. *The Sequence:* Tap the 8 points (Eye, Side of Eye, Under Eye, Under Nose, Chin, Collarbone, Under Arm, Top of Head) while repeating a reminder phrase.
  3. *Integration:* Deep breath and reassessment of the intensity (SUDs).
]
